message: Warning signs of human trafficking include: a sudden increase in money and expensive clothes, unexplained absences from usual activities, sexualized behavior, frequently falling asleep in class, new tattoos, brags about having or making a lot of money, becomes withdrawn, depressed or distracted. Tattoos are used by traffickers to brand victims.

attachments.media_description: Freedom Week brings awareness of human trafficking, domestic violence signs | The Clanton Advertiser
